Interface KnowledgeAsset

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Elevatable, Immutable, ImmutableSource, KnowledgeResource, KnowledgeResourceLike, KnowledgeSource, KnowledgeSourceLike, Lowerable, Source, SourceLike
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    BasicKnowledgeAsset, StructuredKnowledgeAsset
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractKnowledgeAsset, CanonicalBasicKnowledgeAsset, CanonicalKnowledgeAsset

    public interface KnowledgeAsset
extends KnowledgeResource, Lowerable
    Interface for knowledge assets, which are lowerable knowledge resources in a focused preserving environment at the KnowledgeSourceLevel.ASSET abstraction level.
    Author:
    taraathan
